1,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T20:13:22.000Z","msg":"係咪25仔"},{"pid":"0cade88ea3e147ab2caf3707d60b1c5cf3c077a4","tid":893640,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T20:16:45.000Z","msg":"條友根本唔識法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfc70fd2c2adc07efa122bc77dea0b6db94891a","tid":893640,"uid":182638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T20:25:27.000Z","msg":"支那又臝"},{"pid":"a4f1062fa7ee12205d373bb020ef513b8e1bb50c","tid":893640,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:36:54.000Z","msg":"You are fired<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5377e67f24a0a71dce168b9ba573ab415ee450d5","tid":893640,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:50:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國司法部長塞申斯宣佈辭職 大麻股應聲瘋漲</span><br />\n<br />\n新浪美股訊 北京時間11月8日，美國司法部長塞申斯（Jeff Sessions）在特朗普多次抨擊後辭職。大麻股今日大漲，塞申斯曾被媒體稱為&ldquo;大麻的敵人&rdquo;。而塞申斯的幕僚長Matthew G． Whitaker將出任代理司法部部長。<br />\n<br />\n　　總部位於加拿大的Tilray股價上漲30%，離華爾街交易結束僅剩不到一小時。 Canopy Growth和Aurora Cannabis分別增長5.6%和6.5%。<br />\n<br />\n　　<span style=\"color: red;\">塞申斯上任以來，多次表明反對大麻娛樂化。針對暴力事件中使用大麻的現象越來越普遍。塞申斯此前表示：&ldquo;我們國家需要再次說清楚，使用毒品會毀了你的生活。&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n　　B． Riley FBR首席市場策略師阿特-霍根（Art Hogan）表示，&ldquo;如果你做多了大麻股庫存，你會很開心。他（塞申斯）是將大麻合法化擴大到全國的最大障礙。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　"},{"pid":"bf75f35e91c6a8857a76edc878583ac5117a044e","tid":893640,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:55:36.000Z","msg":"支那又贏"},{"pid":"ad2fbe66d6d320d8058cb59da76038863f04305e","tid":893640,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cade88ea3e147ab2caf3707d60b1c5cf3c077a4","tid":893640,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0